Redis Module Structure
======================

redis/
│
├── 📄 redis.config.js              # Redis connection & configuration
├── 📄 index.js                     # Central exports (use this for imports!)
├── 📄 README.md                    # Module documentation
├── 📄 REDIS-CACHE-IMPLEMENTATION.md # Implementation guide
│
├── 📁 cache/                       # Data Caching Services
│   │
│   ├── 🆕 userProfileCache.service.js          # User profiles (30 min TTL)
│   ├── 🆕 travellerRouteCache.service.js       # Active routes (1 hour TTL)
│   ├── 🆕 parcelRequestCache.service.js        # Parcel requests (30 min TTL)
│   ├── 🆕 bookingStatusCache.service.js        # Booking statuses (15 min - 1 hour TTL)
│   ├── 🆕 kycStatusCache.service.js            # KYC statuses (1 hour TTL)
│   ├── 🆕 notificationCountCache.service.js    # Notification counts (5 min TTL)
│   ├── deviceTokenCache.service.js             # FCM tokens (24 hours TTL)
│   ├── platformSettingsCache.service.js        # Platform settings (1 hour TTL)
│   └── detourCache.service.js                  # Route detours (24 hours TTL)
│
├── 📁 services/                    # Redis-based Services
│   │
│   ├── otp.service.js              # OTP storage & verification
│   ├── tokenBlacklist.service.js   # JWT token blacklisting
│   ├── sessionVersion.service.js   # Session versioning
│   └── redisRealtime.service.js    # Pub/Sub for real-time events
│
└── 📁 utils/                       # Redis Utilities
    │
    └── redisLock.util.js           # Distributed locking

Legend:
🆕 = Newly implemented high-priority cache
📄 = File
📁 = Folder

Total: 15 files organized in 3 categories
